title: Furnished Modern Studio With Natural Light Near UW Campus
posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'Text or call us directly at', 'show contact info', 'Book online at', '<URL>', 'Description', 'DXU is home to 97 cozy studios in the heart of University District.', 'Living space is optimized with large windows, plank floors, and efficiency-style kitchens.', "Most studios offer in-home laundry and those that don't are welcome to use the card-operated machines in the basement.", 'Many upper floor apartments offer stunning views of Mt.  Rainier, The Univeristy of Washington, Capitol Hill, and/or the Downtown Seattle Skyline.', 'Package lockers, additional tenant storage, a bicycle storage room, and a large rooftop patio round out the community amenities.', 'Leasing has begun for Fall 2020!', 'Move ins are available September 15th or earlier depending on availability!!', 'Details', 'Availability date:', 'September 15, 2022', 'Pets:', 'None allowed', 'Pet notes:', 'We happily welcome service animals.', 'Deposit:', '$300', 'Leasing options:', '12 months', 'Leasing notes:', 'Most leases begin in September and are offered on a 12 month term basis only.', 'Application fee:', '$55', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', '(none)', 'Utilities Cost:', 'Based on usage', 'Laundry:', 'Shared, In Home', 'Parking type:', 'Parking notes:', 'Bicycle parking available!', 'Appliances:', 'Refrigerator, Microwave, Range', 'Exterior:', 'Deck', 'Heating/cooling:', 'AC Ports, Forced Air Heat', 'Wiring:', 'High-speed internet, Call Box', 'Facilities and Recreation:', 'Barbecue', 'Security and Access:', 'Elevator, Controlled access, Disability access', 'Views:', 'City, Mountain, Water', 'Additional features:', 'Hardwood floor, Non-Smoking Property, Package Lockers', 'Offered by:', 'Blanton Turner - University District Team', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
